## Slash Command Map

| Command | Rule | Purpose |
|---------|------|---------|
| `/generate-overview` | `01_project_overview_generator` | Scan codebase → docs/project_overview.md |
| `/tdd` | `02_tdd_generator` | Feature description → TDD document |
| `/breakdown` | `03_breakdown_generator` | TDD file → task checklist |
| `/implement` | `04_implementation` | Task checklist → code |
| `/task` | `05_quick_task_creator` | Quick task (skip TDD) |
| `/flow` | `06_flow_diagram_generator` | Flow / sequence diagrams |
| `/report` | `07_report_generator` | Project reports |
| `/plan` | `08_plan_generator` | SPEC → implementation plan |
| `/dotnet-review` | `09_dotnet_review` | Expert .NET code review (MySQL/PG aware) |

### CodeGraph MCP Tools (nếu `.codegraph/` có trong project)

| Tool | Khi nào dùng |
|------|-------------|
| `codegraph_explore` | Hiểu một feature/flow — thay thế việc đọc nhiều files |
| `codegraph_search` | Tìm symbol theo tên — thay thế grep |
| `codegraph_find_refs` | Tìm tất cả usages của interface/method |
| `codegraph_impact` | Impact analysis trước khi refactor |

> **Luôn thử CodeGraph trước** khi dùng grep/glob/Read trên source files.
> CodeGraph = 1-3 tool calls thay vì 10-20 file reads.

---

## After Every Implementation Task

1. Update checklist: `[ ]` → `[x]`
2. Suggest Conventional Commit:
   - `feat(scope): what was added`
   - `fix(scope): what was fixed`
   - `refactor(scope): what was cleaned`
3. When ALL tasks done → remind: `💡 Run /handoff in Claude Code for expert review.`

---

## Golden Rule

Do NOT modify source code from a raw requirement.  
Always follow: `/tdd` → `/breakdown` → `/implement`
Always read `docs/project_overview.md` before implement — contains DB provider, patterns, naming.  
Shortcut for small tasks: `/task` (bug fix, CRUD < 1 day)

**CodeGraph rule**: Nếu `.codegraph/` tồn tại → dùng `codegraph_explore` / `codegraph_search` trước khi Read source files.  
Mục tiêu: tối thiểu tool calls, tối đa context quality.
